{"title":"花","authors":["莫文征"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":3,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫文征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虬枝里显现着土的旅历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请把我栽在广袤的原野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我将献给你十倍的美丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她是一切色彩的母体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请把我栽在当阳之处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美的收成将丰硕无比"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱水分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她给予我生命的羽翼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋日里将以涌泉相报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假如春天赐我以涓滴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱修剪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿塑一个强健的躯体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但千万莫把壮枝修剪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那只会带来衰颓凋敝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我永不叹息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦难中更应奔赴花期"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使酷暑奇寒一同压来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美的生命绝不会窒息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我虽不歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沐浴喜悦我永不忘记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对于付出心血的栽培"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的贡献将无限壮丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我永远快乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烦恼和忧伤深埋心底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面向我所热爱的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远绽放着春的笑意"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}